# Movie Review Website

This dynamic website allows users to review movies by adding them to a database, 
along with personal ratings and reviews. The website features user sign-up and login functionality, 
allowing personalized experiences and secure access to reviews and ratings. PHP and MySQL are used to 
handle backend logic and database management. The website supports full CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) 
operations on movie records, enabling users to manage their reviews.

Key features include:

User Authentication: Users can sign up, log in, and manage their accounts.
Movie Database: Users can add, amend, and delete movie entries, along with their personal reviews.
Search Functionality: Users can search for movies based on multiple criteria (e.g., genre, release year, rating).
Cookies & Sessions: Cookies store user preferences, and sessions maintain user state across visits.
Ajax Support: Autocomplete and form assistance improve user experience.
MySQL Database Integration: All movie and user data is stored securely in a MySQL database.
The website is designed to be flexible and user-friendly, offering a seamless experience for managing movie reviews. 
Further enhancements could include better personalization features, error prevention measures and UX.

